title: Kardashian Family Returns to Las Vegas to Support Lamar Odom
text:
> News Kardashian Family Returns to Las Vegas to Support Lamar Odom The Kardashians return to Las Vegas to visit Lamar Odom in the hospital, and send messages of support on social media.
